BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-19-jeff-pitchell-all-stars-7f0b74b7@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260619T230000Z
DTEND:20260620T010000Z
SUMMARY:Jeff Pitchell All Stars at Scullers Jazz Club
LOCATION:400 Soldiers Field Rd\, Boston\, MA 02134
DESCRIPTION:Jeff Pitchell (b. 1966\, Hartford\, CT) is an American blues si
 nger-songwriter and guitarist who leads Jeff Pitchell & Texas Flood. Induc
 ted into the Connecticut Blues Hall of Fame\, his style blends B.B. King a
 nd Duane Allman\; his album 'Heavy Hitter' (Pyramid/EMI) reached #7 on the
  Billboard charts\, and his song 'An Eye for an Eye' was recorded by John 
 Mayall. Tickets: https://www.ticketweb.com/search?q=jeff+pitchell+scullers
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-19-club-d-elf-with-lyle-brewer-and-mister-rourke-early-show-843701de@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260619T233000Z
DTEND:20260620T013000Z
SUMMARY:Club d'Elf with Lyle Brewer and Mister Rourke (Early Show) at Jazz 
 Boston Calendar
LOCATION:Lizard Lounge\, Cambridge
DESCRIPTION:Club d'Elf is a long-running Boston-based collective led by bas
 sist and sintir/guimbri player Mike Rivard (Berklee grad\; ex-Morphine\, E
 ither/Orchestra). For over 25 years the band has fused Moroccan trance\, d
 ub\, electronica\, jazz and improvised funk with a rotating cast of guests
 . Tickets: https://jazzboston.org/jazz-calendar?club-d-elf-live-at-the-liz
 ard-lounge-with-lyle-brewer-and-mister-rourke-early-show&event_id=424063&f
 id=1
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-19-edmar-castaneda-quartet-70ce9e6a@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260619T233000Z
DTEND:20260620T013000Z
SUMMARY:Edmar Castaneda Quartet at Regattabar
LOCATION:1 Bennett St\, Cambridge\, MA 02138
DESCRIPTION:Colombian-born jazz harpist widely regarded as the pre-eminent 
 virtuoso of the jazz harp\, playing melody and bass simultaneously on the 
 Llanera harp. He is a Grammy nominee as part of BEATrio (with Béla Fleck 
 and Antonio Sánchez) and a Latin Grammy nominee\, and has performed with 
 Wynton Marsalis\, John Scofield and at Jazz at Lincoln Center. Tickets: ht
 tps://www.ticketweb.com/venue/regattabar-cambridge-ma/748814
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-20-greg-abate-quartet-fccbfc9e@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260620T230000Z
DTEND:20260621T010000Z
SUMMARY:Greg Abate Quartet at Scullers Jazz Club
LOCATION:400 Soldiers Field Rd\, Boston\, MA 02134
DESCRIPTION:Greg Abate (b. 1947\, Fall River\, MA) is a Berklee-trained beb
 op and hard-bop saxophonist who held the lead alto chair in the Ray Charle
 s Band (1973-74) and later played with the revived Artie Shaw Orchestra. A
  prolific international touring artist\, he has recorded extensively\, inc
 luding on the Candid jazz label\, and was inducted into the Rhode Island M
 usic Hall of Fame (2016). Tickets: https://www.ticketweb.com/event/greg-ab
 ate-quartet-scullers-jazz-club-tickets/14857513
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-20-kinga-glyk-09de5ef4@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260620T230000Z
DTEND:20260621T010000Z
SUMMARY:Kinga Glyk at Jazz Boston Calendar
LOCATION:Regattabar\, Cambridge
DESCRIPTION:Kinga Glyk (b. 1997\, Rydultowy\, Poland) is a Polish electric-
 bass virtuoso and composer who rose to international fame after a 2016 vid
 eo of her playing 'Tears in Heaven' went viral. She is signed to Warner Mu
 sic\, releasing 'Dream' (2017) and 'Real Life' (2024\, co-produced by Snar
 ky Puppy's Michael League). Tickets: https://jazzboston.org/jazz-calendar?
 kinga-glyk&event_id=421271&fid=1
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
