DTSTART:20260620T230000Z
DTEND:20260621T010000Z
SUMMARY:Kinga Głyk at Regattabar
LOCATION:1 Bennett St\, Cambridge\, MA 02138
DESCRIPTION:Kinga Glyk (b. 1997\, Rydultowy\, Poland) is a Polish electric-
 bass virtuoso and composer who rose to international fame after a 2016 vid
 eo of her playing 'Tears in Heaven' went viral. She is signed to Warner Mu
 sic\, releasing 'Dream' (2017) and 'Real Life' (2024\, co-produced by Snar
 ky Puppy's Michael League). Tickets: https://www.ticketweb.com/venue/regat
 tabar-cambridge-ma/748814
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-20-southern-avenue-10cf403a@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260621T000000Z
DTEND:20260621T020000Z
SUMMARY:Southern Avenue at Jazz Boston Calendar
LOCATION:The Center for Arts in Natick\, Natick
DESCRIPTION:Memphis-based blues\, soul and gospel-flavored roots band front
 ed by vocalist Tierinii Jackson and guitarist Ori Naftaly. Their 2025 Alli
 gator Records debut Family earned a Best Contemporary Blues Album nominati
 on at the 2026 Grammys\, their second Grammy nod after 2019's Keep On. Tic
 kets: https://jazzboston.org/jazz-calendar?southern-avenue&event_id=424956
 &fid=1
CATEGORIES:blues
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-20-tarbox-ramblers-with-special-guest-jim-fitting-130eb801@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260621T000000Z
DTEND:20260621T020000Z
SUMMARY:Tarbox Ramblers with Special Guest Jim Fitting at Jazz Boston Calen
 dar
LOCATION:Lizard Lounge\, Cambridge
DESCRIPTION:The Tarbox Ramblers are a Boston/Cambridge-based roots and coun
 try-blues band formed in 1994 and led by slide guitarist and singer Michae
 l Tarbox. Built on early-20th-century blues\, gospel and Appalachian mater
 ial plus Tarbox originals\, they released two acclaimed albums on Rounder 
 Records and drew raves from the New Yorker and Washington Post. Tickets: h
 ttps://jazzboston.org/jazz-calendar?tarbox-ramblers-live-at-the-lizard-lou
 nge-w-special-guest-jim-fitting&event_id=424048&fid=1
CATEGORIES:blues
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-21-ensemble-eclectica-9d0a369d@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260621T163000Z
DTEND:20260621T183000Z
SUMMARY:Ensemble Eclectica at Jazz Boston Calendar
LOCATION:Arlington Visitor Center\, Arlington
DESCRIPTION:Ensemble Eclectica is a Boston-area jazz ensemble that performs
  jazz improvisations on older songs\, featuring vocalist Louise Grasmere a
 nd appearing at venues such as Fivesparks\; it maintains its own site but 
 has little broader press footprint. Tickets: https://jazzboston.org/jazz-c
 alendar?free-concert-by-ensemble-eclectica-at-the-arlington-tiny-shed-seri
 es&event_id=423477&fid=1
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-21-antonia-bennett-a8d8118b@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260621T200000Z
DTEND:20260621T220000Z
SUMMARY:Antonia Bennett at Jazz Boston Calendar
LOCATION:Regattabar\, Cambridge
DESCRIPTION:Antonia Bennett (b. 1974) is an American jazz and standards voc
 alist\, the youngest child of Tony Bennett. Berklee-trained and also schoo
 led at the Lee Strasberg Theatre Institute\, she carries forward the Great
  American Songbook tradition\; the New York Times described her voice as '
 Billie Holiday and Rickie Lee Jones\, with a hint of Betty Boop.' Tickets:
  https://jazzboston.org/jazz-calendar?antonia-bennett-fathers-day-concert&
 event_id=415193&fid=1
CATEGORIES:vocal jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-21-jorge-perez-albela-group-aa1c40fe@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260621T200000Z
DTEND:20260621T220000Z
SUMMARY:The Jorge Perez-Albela Group at Jazz Boston Calendar
LOCATION:The Lilypad\, Cambridge
DESCRIPTION:Jorge Perez-Albela is a Lima-born\, Boston-based Latin jazz dru
 mmer/percussionist and educator\, a Berklee Global Jazz Institute graduate
  and faculty member known for his Afro-Peruvian cajon work and sideman cre
 dits with Maria Schneider\, Danilo Perez\, Bert Seager and Sofia Rei. Tick
 ets: https://jazzboston.org/jazz-calendar?the-jorge-perez-albela-group&eve
 nt_id=425081&fid=1
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-21-dad-jazz-jesse-taitt-trio-791f165a@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260621T230000Z
DTEND:20260622T010000Z
SUMMARY:Dad Jazz + Jesse Taitt Trio at Jazz Boston Calendar
LOCATION:The Square Root\, Roslindale
DESCRIPTION:Dad Jazz appears to be a small Boston-area jazz group with litt
 le public footprint\; web searches surface several unrelated acts of simil
 ar name (a Bellingham WA band\, Chicago Jazz Dads\, etc.) and no national 
 credentials for a Boston jazz outfit by this name. Tickets: https://jazzbo
 ston.org/jazz-calendar?jazz-sunday-dad-jazz-jesse-taitt-trio&event_id=4249
 90&fid=1
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
