DTEND:20260626T010000Z
SUMMARY:Victor Wooten & The Wooten Brothers at Jimmy's Jazz & Blues Club
LOCATION:135 Congress St\, Portsmouth\, NH 03801
DESCRIPTION:Five-time Grammy-winning electric bassist and founding member o
 f Béla Fleck & The Flecktones\, widely regarded as one of the greatest ba
 ss players alive. Rolling Stone named him among the Top 10 Bassists of All
  Time\, and he has been voted Bass Player magazine's Bassist of the Year t
 hree times. Tickets: https://jimmysoncongress.com/event/victor-wooten-the-
 wooten-brothers-2/
CATEGORIES:jazz
