UID:e-2026-06-26-emmet-cohen-trio-441884f2@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260626T230000Z
DTEND:20260627T010000Z
SUMMARY:Emmet Cohen Trio at Scullers Jazz Club
LOCATION:400 Soldiers Field Rd\, Boston\, MA 02134
DESCRIPTION:Acclaimed jazz pianist and Mack Avenue recording artist known f
 or his Masters Legacy Series and the popular 'Live From Emmet's Place' liv
 estream series. A Thelonious Monk Competition finalist and 2019 American P
 ianists Awards winner\, he was named DownBeat Readers Poll Pianist of the 
 Year in 2025. Tickets: https://www.ticketweb.com/search?q=emmet+cohen+scul
 lers
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-26-alex-gao-becoming-80c4a420@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260626T233000Z
DTEND:20260627T013000Z
SUMMARY:Alex Gao: Becoming at Regattabar
LOCATION:1 Bennett St\, Cambridge\, MA 02138
DESCRIPTION:Alex Gao (高紫旗) is a Boston/Berklee-affiliated vocalist an
 d bandleader whose project 'Becoming' is a genre-blending musical portrait
  of a young Asian-American woman\, fusing pop\, jazz\, world music and ava
 nt-garde reimaginings of covers and originals. The project has featured no
 table sidemen such as drummer Francisco Mela. Tickets: https://www.ticketw
 eb.com/venue/regattabar-cambridge-ma/748814
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-26-eddie-9v-ad95edb7@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260626T233000Z
DTEND:20260627T013000Z
SUMMARY:Eddie 9V at Jimmy's Jazz & Blues Club
LOCATION:135 Congress St\, Portsmouth\, NH 03801
DESCRIPTION:Atlanta-born blues and soul singer/guitarist (real name Brooks 
 Mason) steeped in classic blues and Southern soul. His albums Little Black
  Flies and the #1-charting Capricorn drew wide acclaim\; he records for Ru
 f Records and has earned Blues Blast Music Award and Blues Music Award nom
 inations. Tickets: https://jimmysoncongress.com/event/eddie-9v/
CATEGORIES:blues
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-26-albert-cummings-01b0c236@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260627T000000Z
DTEND:20260627T020000Z
SUMMARY:Albert Cummings at Jazz Boston Calendar
LOCATION:Spire Center for the Performing Arts\, Plymouth
DESCRIPTION:Massachusetts-born blues guitarist\, singer and songwriter in t
 he Stevie Ray Vaughan / Albert King / Hendrix lineage\, with multiple #1 a
 nd #2 Billboard Blues chart albums (Ten\, Strong\, Someone Like You). His 
 live record earned a Blues Music Award nomination for Blues Rock Album\, a
 nd he records for the Mascot Label Group (Provogue/Ivy Music). Tickets: ht
 tps://jazzboston.org/jazz-calendar?albert-cummings&event_id=419751&fid=1
CATEGORIES:blues
END:VEVENT
