BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-27-vapors-of-morphine-with-special-guest-le-prestige-578f721a@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260627T230000Z
DTEND:20260628T010000Z
SUMMARY:Vapors of Morphine with Special Guest Le Prestige at Regattabar
LOCATION:1 Bennett St\, Cambridge\, MA 02138
DESCRIPTION:Vapors of Morphine is an American 'low rock' band formed in 200
 9 by surviving Morphine members Dana Colley (baritone sax) and Jerome Deup
 ree (drums) with blues guitarist Jeremy Lyons\, carrying forward the late 
 Mark Sandman's signature low-rock/blues sound. The current lineup pairs Co
 lley and Lyons with drummer Tom Arey. Tickets: https://www.ticketweb.com/v
 enue/regattabar-cambridge-ma/748814
CATEGORIES:blues
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-28-ana-popovic-0fd4ef54@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260628T233000Z
DTEND:20260629T013000Z
SUMMARY:Ana Popovic at Jimmy's Jazz & Blues Club
LOCATION:135 Congress St\, Portsmouth\, NH 03801
DESCRIPTION:Serbian-born\, Los Angeles-based blues-rock guitarist\, singer 
 and songwriter with a long international career and numerous Billboard Blu
 es chart-topping albums. An 8-time Blues Music Award nominee (Contemporary
  Blues Female Artist\, Blues Rock Artist)\, though without a confirmed BMA
  win\; her 2023 album Power was released on the independent ArtisteXclusiv
 e label. Tickets: https://jimmysoncongress.com/event/ana-popovic/
CATEGORIES:blues
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-29-local-artist-series-tim-theriault-3c75d8f6@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260629T230000Z
DTEND:20260630T010000Z
SUMMARY:Local Artist Series: Tim Theriault at Jimmy's Jazz & Blues Club
LOCATION:135 Congress St\, Portsmouth\, NH 03801
DESCRIPTION:Tim Theriault is a New England blues guitarist and vocalist wit
 h over 25 years on the Seacoast (NH/Maine) music scene\, having played in 
 bands including Crossfire\, Heavens to Murgatroid and Four Sticks as well 
 as his own Tim Theriault Duo & Band. Tickets: https://jimmysoncongress.com
 /event/local-artist-series-tim-theriault/
CATEGORIES:blues
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e-2026-06-30-kamasi-washington-1900-506e95af@jazz-weekly.bitdoktor.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260619T020521Z
DTSTART:20260630T230000Z
DTEND:20260701T010000Z
SUMMARY:Kamasi Washington at Jimmy's Jazz & Blues Club
LOCATION:135 Congress St\, Portsmouth\, NH 03801
DESCRIPTION:Los Angeles tenor saxophonist\, composer and bandleader whose o
 rchestral\, genre-blending records (The Epic\, Heaven and Earth) made him 
 a defining figure of 21st-century jazz. He contributed to Kendrick Lamar's
  To Pimp a Butterfly and scored Michelle Obama's Netflix documentary Becom
 ing. Tickets: https://jimmysoncongress.com/event/kamasi-washington-2/
CATEGORIES:jazz
END:VEVENT
